  "instructions": [
    "In a large saucepan, heat the vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the butter and score-fat, stirring until the fat is fully incorporated and melted.",
    "Add the butter-infused popcorn seasoning and stir for 30 seconds.",
    "Add the all-purpose flour and cook for 1-2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Slowly pour in the chicken broth, whisking continuously to avoid lumps.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until it thickens.",
    "Stir in the salt-free seasoning and cook for an additional 1-2 minutes.",
    "Add the toffee popcorn and stir to coat with the pilaf mixture.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the pilaf hot, garnished with chopped parsley."
  ],
